==Introduction==

These a brief notes on how to install an [[Managed_Web_Server_version_3|MWSv3]] panel server. It's basically just a case of running ansible with the mwsserver role, with a couple of issues round secrets

===TLS key and certificate===

These live in <code>/data/certs</code> and <code>/data/keys</code>. Extract these from the backups of the previous instance.

===send_nsca configuration===

For the passive nagios checks to work, you need to configure <code>/etc/send_nsca.cfg</code> to know the credentials for Platforms' Nagios instance. The relevant things to put in that file are documented [[Platforms_Nagios#Passive_checks_using_NSCA|here]].